description: The goal of the CPTAC, TCGA Cancer Proteome Study of Colorectal Tissue is to analyze the proteomes of TCGA tumor samples that have been comprehensively characterized by molecular methods. Ninety-five TCGA tumor samples were used in this study.

terms.name: Reference
terms.value: Slebos RJ, Wang X, Wang X, Zhang B, Tabb DL, Liebler DC. Proteomic analysis of colon and rectal carcinoma using standard and customized databases. Sci Data. 2015 Jun 23;2:150022. eCollection 2015

title: CPTAC proteomic analysis of TCGA colon and rectal carcinomas using standard and customized databases, part 10
